    Scope and Contents
SPRINGFIELD RACE RIOT 
Brittin, a resident of Sherman, Illinois, relates a second hand account of the 1908 race riot. He discusses his uncle's involvement, lynchings and destruction in the city of Springfield. 1 tape, 90 mins., 5 pp. 
Interview by Cullom Davis, 1972 
